			<p>
				The EclipseLink DBWS component enables Java developers a
				declarative Web Service solution for accessing
				relational databases. The DBWS Builder generates the
				necessary configuration files based on the provided
				database artifacts so that EclipseLink's relational and
				persistence services can be combined to handle the
				requests.
